    {
      "item_id": "536d47d380:10",
      "text": "tractor query",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "536d47d380:16",
      "text": "默认名称为 admin、rush、default、batch。",
      "ascii_letters": 21,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "536d47d380:18",
      "text": "Custom 菜单操作（Custom Menu Actions）",
      "ascii_letters": 23,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "536d47d380:20",
      "text": "Job Authoring API（作业编写 API）",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "536d47d380:21",
      "text": "-- 新的 tractor.api.author 模块允许 Python 脚本轻松创建 Job、Task 和 Command 对象，并按照依赖关系需求把它们链接起来。随后 Job.spool() 方法会把生成的 job 发送到 tractor-engine 的 job queue。",
      "ascii_letters": 68,
      "cjk_chars": 44
    },
    {
      "item_id": "536d47d380:23",
      "text": "-- 面向小型工作室的新简单 zero-config 通告能力，允许 tractor-blades 和其他 Tractor 工具在本地网络中找到 tractor-engine，而不需要手动修改 nameserver（DNS/LDAP）配置。在管理员已经在站点 nameserver 数据库中创建主机名别名 tractor-engine 的工作室里，tractor-engine 会自动禁用这种 SSDP-style 流量。",
      "ascii_letters": 105,
      "cjk_chars": 74
    },
    {
      "item_id": "536d47d380:24",
      "text": "Checkpoint-Resume（检查点-恢复）支持",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "536d47d380:25",
      "text": "-- 对 job scripting、dispatching 和 Dashboard 的新扩展，增加了与增量计算相关的有用能力。Tractor 还支持通用的 retry from last checkpoint 机制。这两项功能都与新的 RenderMan 19 RIS checkpoint 和 incremental rendering 功能集成。",
      "ascii_letters": 104,
      "cjk_chars": 43
    },
    {
      "item_id": "536d47d380:26",
      "text": "Blade Auto-Update（Blade 自动更新）",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "536d47d380:28",
      "text": "Pluggable Authentication Module（PAM，可插拔认证模块）支持",
      "ascii_letters": 32,
      "cjk_chars": 9
    },
    {
      "item_id": "536d47d380:32",
      "text": "EngineOwner",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "536d47d380:34",
      "text": "动态 Service Key 能力通告",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "536d47d380:35",
      "text": "-- 新增了几个 blade profile",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "536d47d380:36",
      "text": "\"Provides\"",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "536d47d380:38",
      "text": "Resource Usage Tracking（资源使用情况跟踪）",
      "ascii_letters": 21,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "536d47d380:39",
      "text": "-- CPU、RSS 和 VSZ",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 1
    },
    {
      "item_id": "536d47d380:41",
      "text": "process metrics 现在会记录到每个已启动 command 的 job database 中。目前支持 Linux 和 OSX tractor-blades。",
      "ascii_letters": 53,
      "cjk_chars": 18
    },
    {
      "item_id": "536d47d380:48",
      "text": "Automatic Blade Error Throttle（Blade 自动错误节流）",
      "ascii_letters": 32,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "536d47d380:50",
      "text": "Job Spooling（作业提交）改进",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    }
  ],
